10#include <stdio.h>
11#include "internal/cryptlib.h"
12#include <openssl/evp.h>
13#include <openssl/dh.h>
14
15#ifndef OPENSSL_NO_STDIO
16int DHparams_print_fp(FILE *fp, const DH *x)
17{
18 BIO *b;
19 int ret;
20
21 if ((b = BIO_new(BIO_s_file())) == NULL) {
22 DHerr(DH_F_DHPARAMS_PRINT_FP, ERR_R_BUF_LIB);
23 return 0;
24 }
25 BIO_set_fp(b, fp, BIO_NOCLOSE);
26 ret = DHparams_print(b, x);
27 BIO_free(b);
28 return ret;
29}
30#endif
